title: Hour 1 - Derek Jeter Doc, LLWS Sportsmanship
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Derek Jeter Doc, LLWS Sportsmanship
description:
Dan wishes professional athletes would take their cue from the Little League World Series with regard to sportsmanship, and he talks about the latest documentary about the Yankees featuring Derek Jeter.
